---
title: Sausage and Broccolini Pasta with Fresh Penne
description: Sausage and broccolini unite to make one of the tastiest pasta dishes you didn't know you were missing in your life! And all wrapped up and ready to eat in 20 minutes, we feel confident to let the food do the talking!
